dc_title_s: Pittsfield: township no. 3 south range no. 6 east.
dc_description_s: Map shows Pittsfield Township, Michigan. Property owners and location of map are handwritten on a printed template. "Presented to the Washtenaw Co. Pioneer Society by L.G. Risdon, May 20th 1885" written on verso of map. 1 map; 31 x 31 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
